videoSnippet.title: Capablanca is Sad His Opponent Didn't Play the Best Moves || Rice Memorial (1916)

Jose Raul Capablanca vs Alfred Schroeder
Rice Memorial (1916), New York, NY USA, rd 10, Jan-29 
Queen's Gambit Declined: Orthodox Defense. Henneberger Variation (D63)

1. d4 d5 2. Nf3 e6 3. c4 Nf6 4. Nc3 Nbd7 5. Bg5 Be7 6. e3 O-O 7. Rc1 a6 8. Qc2 Re8 9. Bd3 dc4 10. Bc4 b5 11. Bd3 Bb7 12. a4 b4 13. Bf6 Nf6 14. Ne4 Ne4 15. Be4 Be4 16. Qe4 c5 17. dc5 Qa5 18. b3 Bc5 19. Ng5 h6 20. Qh7 Kf8 21. Qh8 Ke7 22. Qg7 hg5 23. Qg5 Kd6 24. Ke2 Rac8 25. Rc4 Kc6 26. Rhc1 Kb6 27. h4 f5 28. Qg7 Re7 29. Qe5 Rc6 30. Rc5
